channel.title: Default Gateway Problem!
channel.description: Yes, I am setting up my server again, and i switched computers. Well, i have a problem...My ipconfig command isnt working inside of my cmd window I type in ipconfig [enter] and it says "ipconfig.exe is not a valid win32 application. access denied. What the heck is going on? I just want a way to figure out my default ip thats all. Please help!
